reviewText: They could have dropped two of the women, but the rest of the DVD is very good.

They offered a nice mix of "The girl next door" as well as professional stars. You can really tell that some of them are new to the scene but are eager to show you their "assets". On the other hand, there is very steamy scene with Carmel Moore, once of the best stars in the business and she really shows you why she's earned a spot on the cover. The host was Kymberly Jane I don't think she's an adult star but she did a decent job at introducing the scenes and a much better job at "performing" for you. I think it's well worth it.
